ntent/uploads/2023/08/Peter-Jackson-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-jackson">彼得·杰克逊</a>将<em>《跟我说话》</em>描述为他多年来看过的“最好、最激烈”的恐怖电影。</p><p>这位因执导<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lord-of-the-rings"><em>《指环王》</em></a>和<em>《霍比特人》</em>三部曲而闻名的导演，在通过发行商 Ahi Films 发表的一份声明中赞扬了这部突破性的澳大利亚恐怖电影。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/talk-to-me-review-horror-3474833">《跟我说话》评论：为这部令人毛骨悚然的恐怖片首映提供帮助</a></strong></li></ul><p>“这是无情的可怕和令人不安的——以最好的方式，”杰克逊说（通过<a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/peter-jackson-talk-to-me-best-horror-movie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TotalFilm</em></a> ）。 “《<em>跟我说话》</em>不仅好，而且非常好。这是我多年来看过的最好、最激烈的恐怖电影。”</p><p>在<em>拍摄《指环王》</em>之前，杰克逊最出名的是执导喜剧恐怖片，如<em>《脑死亡》</em> 、 <em>《坏品味》</em>和<em>《惊魂者》</em> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="跟我说话|官方预告片高清 | A24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aLAKJu9aJys?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>其他一些知名导演也对<em>《跟我说话》</em>赞不绝口，其中包括乔丹·皮尔（ <em>《逃出绝命镇</em>》），他打电话给导演丹尼和迈克尔·菲利普，告诉他们这部电影“启发”了他。</p><p> “这真的是有史以来最疯狂的事情，”迈克尔在谈到给皮尔的电话时告诉<a href="https://www.ign.com/videos/jordan-peele-called-talk-to-mes-directors-after-being-inspired-by-the-movie-comic-con-2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>IGN</em></a> 。 “我拿着电话浑身发抖，这真是令人心碎。”</p><p> 《<em>跟我说话》</em>由索菲亚·王​​尔德主演，讲述了一群青少年发现他们可以用一只神秘的防腐手与灵魂接触的故事，结果事情却失控。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/talk-to-me-review-horror-3474833">四星评论</a>中写道：“铁杆恐怖迷们不应该期待一场血腥屠杀的全面盛宴，而应该期待更多与阿里·阿斯特或乔丹·皮尔的前两部电影相一致的新派令人不寒而栗的电影。无论如何：如果想要观看来自澳大利亚的顶级夏季恐怖节目，请不要错过<em>《跟我说话</em>》。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/peter-jackson-praises-best-most-intense-horror-movie-seen-in-years-3483452">彼得·杰克逊称赞他多年来看过的“最好、最激烈的恐怖电影”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
这是“芭比娃娃”被禁止的每个国家https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-every-country-barbie-banned-3483447?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=heres-every-country-barbie-bannedAdam Starkey Tue, 15 Aug 2023 18:49:40 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3483447 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="芭比 瑞恩·高斯林 玛格特·罗比" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在阿尔及利亚，这部电影因“宣扬同性恋”而被撤下</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-every-country-barbie-banned-3483447">《这里是所有禁止“芭比娃娃”的国家》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="芭比 瑞恩·高斯林 玛格特·罗比" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格蕾塔·葛韦格饰演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比娃娃</em></a>在上映后在多个国家被禁。</p><p>这部由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林</a>主演的奇幻喜剧已成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-are-highest-grossing-movies-2023-3478504">2023 年全球第二高票房电影</a>，仅次于<em>《超级马里奥兄弟大电影》</em> ，本月初票房突破 10 亿美元大关。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影的成功也跨越了另一个里程碑，成为票房最高的完全由女性导演的真人电影。</p><h2><em>芭比</em>在哪里被禁止了？</h2><p>在 7 月份上映之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-banned-in-vietnam-over-offending-south-china-sea-map-3464538"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em>在越南被禁</a>，因为其中的一个场景是描绘中国在南海有争议的领土主张的地图。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/barbie-movie-banned-vietnam-map-south-china-sea-rcna92314" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>报道，这一场景展示了“九段线”的“令人反感的图像”，中国地图上用这条线来说明其对南海大片地区的主权主张，越南对南海有争议。 </p><figure id="attachment_3470023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470023" style="width: 1615px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3470023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530.jpg" alt="芭比" width="1615" height="1030" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530.jpg 1615w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1392x888.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1068x681.jpg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-768x490.jpg 768w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1536x980.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3470023" class="wp-caption-text">瑞恩·高斯林和玛格特·罗比在《芭比娃娃》中。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>最近，许多电影因同样的原因在该国被禁，包括索尼的<em>《神秘海域》</em>和梦工厂的动画电影<em>《雪人奇缘》</em> 。</p><p>科威特<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/10/arts/barbie-ban-kuwait-lebanon.html#:~:text=Although%20the%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie%20is%20a%20billion-dollar%20global,feature%20any%20scenes%20that%20overtly%20portray%20same-sex%20relationships." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>新闻</em></a>出版部副部长拉菲·阿尔苏贝埃 (Lafy Al-Subei&#39;e) 表示，由于<em>芭比娃娃</em>宣传了“与科威特社会和公共秩序格格不入的思想和信仰”，科威特随后禁止了该片的上映。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/10/arts/barbie-ban-kuwait-lebanon.html#:~:text=Although%20the%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie%20is%20a%20billion-dollar%20global,feature%20any%20scenes%20that%20overtly%20portray%20same-sex%20relationships." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>约克时报</em></a>）。</p><p>大约在同一时间（8月9日），黎巴嫩文化部长穆罕默德·莫尔塔达（Mohammad Mortada）采取行动禁止<em>芭比娃娃</em>，称这部电影被发现“宣扬同性恋和性转变”。在莫塔达的声明中，他还表示，这部电影降低了家庭单位的重要性，“与信仰和道德价值观相矛盾”（来自<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/aug/09/lebanon-in-move-to-ban-barbie-film-for-promoting-homosexuality" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>）。</p><p>据官方消息人士和当地 24H Algerie 新闻网站（ <a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/algeria-bans-barbie-movie-media-official-source-say-2023-08-14/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>）报道，阿尔及利亚<em>在芭比娃娃</em>在该国发行三周后就对其进行了禁止，理由是它“宣扬同性恋和其他西方越轨行为”。</p><p>华纳兄弟尚未对禁令做出回应。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">四星评论</a>中写道：“接下来是一部细致入微、玫瑰色的喜剧冒险片，配以由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">Lizzo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>主演的令人惊叹的流行配乐，不知怎的，它不辜负巨大的炒作。借用 Ken 最酷的夹克（在长长的阵容中）的双关语，<em>芭比</em>不仅仅是‘足够’。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-every-country-barbie-banned-3483447">《这里是所有禁止“芭比娃娃”的国家》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
